These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
House: modern, cottage
2 different games are played: backgammon, poker
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, disco
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, fonseca
1. the modern house is on the far right##1
2. the fan of indie is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
3. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| House       | cottage       | modern |
| Game         | poker | backgammon  |
| Music-Genre       | disco    | indie    |
| Cigar   | fonseca       | old-henry      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, british
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, rock-climbing
There are 2 different favourite colors: blue, black
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, scooter
1. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes blue is on the right of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Nationality      | british     | colombian |
| Hobby           | magic-tricks | rock-climbing      |
| Color   | black  | blue      |
| Transport         | bus | scooter     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
2 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, davidoff
There are 2 different favourite colors: white, ebony
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, june
1. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
2. the owner of the cat is the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the bongani-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Pet      | cat | goldfish  |
| Cigar          | bongani    | davidoff   |
| Color   | ebony  | white   |
| Birthday     | june     | november |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: iris, orchid
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, oliveros
2 different games are played: chess, poker
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, tram
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
2. the person playing chess is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
3. the person who growsorchid is the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Flower      | iris       | orchid |
| Cigar          | oliveros         | tiparillo    |
| Game           | poker | chess    |
| Transport   | skateboard           | tram   |

