There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, software-developer
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, may
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the software-developer##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |
| City          | hamburg | hannover  |
| Beverage   | 7up   | lemonade     |
| Job         | designer  | software-developer |
| Birthday     | september       | may    |

