1. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
2. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person playing go##1
3. the person who growsorchid is the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| City           | liverpool | rome     |
| Food   | cucumber          | broccoli |
| Flower           | orchid          | zinnia    |
| Game     | go            | canasta       |

 